e%20Dircks%20shows%20a%20U.S.%20Navy%20plane%20that%20overshot%20a%20Marine%20base%20on%20Kaneohe%20Bay%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20Monday%2C%20Nov.%2020%2C%202023.%20An%20official%20says%20all%20nine%20people%20aboard%20the%20plane%20have%20escaped%20injury.%3Cp%3EDiane%20Dircks%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWater%20landings%20%E2%80%94%20also%20called%20ditching%20%E2%80%94%20are%20not%20common%20in%20commercial%20aircraft%2C%20experts%20previously%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-its-hard-for-planes-land-on-water-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20their%20landing%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20execute%20due%20to%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%2C%20like%20wave%20action%20and%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20many%20of%20these%20overshot%20landings%20have%20happened%20on%20land.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkorean-air-plane-damaged-crash-during-landing-overshot-runway-philippines-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKorean%20Air%3C%2Fa%3E%20plane%20overshot%20the%20runway%20after%20attempting%20to%20land%20twice%20and%20heavily%20damaged%20its%20exterior.%20In%202020%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Firanian-plane-skidded-off-runway-onto-city-road-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIranian%20plane%3C%2Fa%3E%20missed%20the%20landing%20strip%20and%20skidded%20onto%20a%20busy%20highway.%20No%20one%20died%20in%20either%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELandings%20are%20statistically%20the%20most%20dangerous%20part%20of%20a%20plane%20trip%20and%20make%20up%2049%25%20of%20fatal%20plane%20accidents.%20This%20is%20because%20when%20planes%20are%20flying%2C%20they%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20course%20correct%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-airplane-takeoff-landing-are-dangerous-flight-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C