312%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%5Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20Hindu%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Canada%20by%20extremist%20elements%20with%20Khalistan%20referendum%20posters%20in%20August%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20on%20the%20temple%20gate%20referred%20to%20and%20also%20had%20the%20picture%20of%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20chief%20and%20designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20such%20attack%20on%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Canada%3B%20multiple%20such%20incidents%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists.%20Several%20incidents%20were%20also%20recorded%20this%20year%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti%20in%20Windsor%2C%20in%20Canada's%20Ontario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Canada's%20Mississauga%20was%20vandalised%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti.%20The%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%20condemned%20the%20defacing%20of%20the%20mandir%20and%20requested%20Canadian%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20the%20incident%20and%20take%20prompt%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Brampton%20was%20defaced%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti%2C%20triggering%20outrage%20among%20the%20Indian%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%20condemned%20the%20vandalism%20at%20the%20Gauri%20Shankar%20Mandir%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20act%20has%20deeply%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20soured%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20during%20a%20debate%20in%20the%20Canadian%20P