ement%20was%20nearing%20a%20truce%20agreement%20with%20Israel%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20Telegram.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20are%20close%20to%20reaching%20a%20deal%20on%20a%20truce%2C%26quot%3B%20Haniyeh%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegotiators%20have%20been%20working%20to%20seal%20a%20deal%20to%20allow%20the%20release%20of%20around%20240%20mostly%20Israeli%20hostages%20seized%20on%20October%207%2C%20during%20the%20deadliest%20assault%20on%20Israel%20in%20its%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20fighters%20also%20killed%20around%201%2C200%20people%20during%20their%20cross-border%20assault%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20a%20relentless%20bombing%20campaign%20and%20ground%20offensive%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20vowing%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Hamas%20government%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20war%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2013%2C300%20people%2C%20thousands%20of%20them%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntense%20negotiations%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%2C%20where%20Hamas%20has%20a%20political%20office%20and%20where%20Haniyeh%20is%20based%2C%20have%20been%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar's%20prime%20minister%20said%20Sunday%20that%20a%20deal%20to%20free%20some%20of%20the%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20a%20temporary%20ceasefire%20hinged%20on%20%26quot%3Bminor%26quot%3B%20practical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20he%20believed%20a%20deal%20to%20free%20the%20hostages%20was%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20when%20asked%20whether%20a%20hostage%20deal%20was%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20then%20crossed%20his%20fingers%20to%20signal%20he%20hoped%20for%20good%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20talks%20told%20AFP%20a%20tentative%