s-first-images-of-workers-stuck-in-uttarkashi-tunnel-4591069%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcamera-through-pipe-gets-first-images-of-workers-stuck-in-uttarkashi-tunnel-4591069%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDar%20Kar%20Khel%20Rahe...%26quot%3B%3A%20Dravid%20Told%20After%20Loss%20In%20WC%20Final.%20His%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20star-studded%20Indian%20batting%20unit%20faltered%20on%20the%20biggest%20stage%20but%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20backed%20his%20players%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20not%20defensive%20and%20game%20circumstances%20dictated%20how%20the%20batters%20went%20about%20their%20job.%20India%20managed%20a%20below-par%20240%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E'%20team%20gunned%20down%20the%20target%20in%2043%20overs%20to%20secure%20a%20record-extending%20sixth%20World%20Cup%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20three%20wickets%20for%2081%20runs%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20(54%20off%2063)%20and%20K%20L%20Rahul%20(66%20off%20107)%20went%20on%20consolidation%20mode%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20where%20the%20hosts%20could%20only%20find%20the%20boundary%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BLast%20year%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20we%20made%20170%20runs%20in%2020%20overs%2C%20and%20England%20chased%20it%20easily.%20Today%20when%20we%20made%20240%20runs%20-%20Australia%20did%20not%20face%20any%20difficulties.%20Rohit%20comes%20on%20this%20wicket%20and%20scores%2045-47%20in%2030%20balls.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20some%20batsmen%20who%20can%20score%2060-65%20runs%20on%20110%20balls.%20And%20the%20strike%20rate%20is%20very%20low.%20So%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20in%20big%20matches%2C%20we%20play%20a%20little%20scared.%20You%20feel%20that%20our%20approach%20is%20not%20right%3F%20What%20are%20the%20issues%3F%20These%20issues%20have%20been%20visible%20since%20the%20last%20three%20or%20four%20World%20Cups%2C%20Asia%20Cups.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Dravid%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20won't%20believe%20that%20we%20played%20with%20fear%20in%20this%20tournament.%20In%20this%20final%20match%2C%20we%20were%20on%2080%20runs%20in%2010%20overs.%20We%20were%20losing%20wickets.%20When%20you%20lose%20wickets%2C%20you%20have%20to%20change%20your%20strategy%20and%20tactics.%20We%20showed%20that%20in%20this%20tournament.%20When%20we%20lost%20against%20England%2C%20we%20played%20differently.%20You%20have%20to%20play.%20You%20start%20with%20front%20foot%20cricket.%20And%20in%20this%20match%2C%20in%20the%20final%2C%20we%20didn't%20play%20anything%20out%20of%20fear.%20They%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20bowling%20in%20the%20middle%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20three%20wickets.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20a%20period%20of%20consolidation.%20But%20whenever%20we%20thought%20we'd%20play%20attacking%20or%20positive%20and%20go%20forward%20and%20hit%2C%20we%20lost%20wickets.%20So%2C%20you%20have%20to%20build%20again.%20Whenever%20you%20have%20a%20partnership%2C%20you%20have%20to%20build%20it.%20You%20saw%20the%20batting%20of%20the%20team.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Marnus%20and%20Head%20were%20playing.%20They%20established%20it.%20But%20they%20didn't%20get%20out%2C%20so%20they%20kept%20playing.%20If%20you%20keep%20losing%20wickets%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20rebuild.%20But%20it's%20not%20like%20we%20started%20playing%20defensively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20who%20last%20won%20an%20ICC%20trophy%20in%202013%2C%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20win%20a%20title%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E-Rahul%20Dravid%20era%20that%20had%20begun%20after%20the%202021%20T20%20World%20Cup%20debacle%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid's%20tenure%20was%20till%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20future%2C%20he%20was%20non-committal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20given%20any%20thought%20to%20next%20year's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what's%20there%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dravid%20referring%20to%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20USA%20and%20Caribbean%20in%20six%20months'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20on%20a%20roll%20in%20this%20tournament%20until%20their%20juggernaut%20was%20ended%20by%20an%20all-round%20Australia%2C%20who%20know%20how%20to%20excel%20on%20the%20biggest%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20led%20from%20the%20front%20with%20his%20bold%20stroke-play%20throughout%20the%20competition%20and%20Dravid%20was%20all%20praise%20for%20him%20and%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20has%20been%20an%20exceptional%20leader%2C%20always%20committed%20to%20planning%20and%20gave%20personal%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20this%20campaign.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20is%20disappointment%2C%20but%20this%20team%20has%20given%20a%20lot%20of%20joy%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20Rohit%20and%20team%20is%20disappointed%2C%20and%20it%20is%20tough%20to%20see%20the%20emotion%20as%20coach%20in%20that%20dressing%20room.%20But%20the%20sun%20will%20come%20up%20tomorrow%2C%20and%20as%20sportsmen%2C%20we%20move%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cst