20Brockman%20said%20in%20his%20post%2C%20were%20conveyed%20by%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20co-founder%20and%20Chief%20Scientist%20at%20OpenAI.%20%26quot%3BSam%20and%20I%20are%20shocked%20and%20saddened%20by%20what%20the%20board%20did%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Brockman%20said%20in%20his%20post%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20Microsoft-backed%20OpenAI%20said%20Altman's%20departure%20follows%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberative%20review%20process%20by%20the%20board%2C%20which%20concluded%20that%20he%20was%20not%20consistently%20candid%20in%20his%20communications%20with%20the%20board%2C%20hindering%20its%20ability%20to%20exercise%20its%20responsibilities%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20board%20no%20longer%20has%20confidence%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20continue%20leading%20OpenAI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20tech%20industry.%20Soon%20after%2C%20US%20media%20reports%20claimed%20that%20major%20investors%20in%20OpenAI%20wanted%20Altman%20to%20return%20and%20had%20started%20efforts%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20him.%20The%20attempts%20to%20bring%20him%20back%2C%20reports%20said%2C%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20after%20Altman%20demanded%20sweeping%20changes%2C%20including%20the%20removal%20of%20current%20board%20members%2C%20as%20a%20condition%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20OpenAI's%20staff%20has%20threatened%20to%20quit%20and%20join%20Altman%20at%20Microsoft's%20new%20division%20unless%20the%20board%20resigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20Mira%20Murati%2C%20Chief%20Data%20Scientist%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20and%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Brad%20Lightcap%2C%20about%20500%20staff%20members%20said%20they%20would%20resign%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700538120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fcbm3qo1o_sam-altman_625x300_17_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht