20of%20Israelis%20but%20the%20freedom%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20for%20the%20international%20community.%20They%20are%20destined%20to%20languish%20in%20the%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20unheard%20and%20unseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-300x158.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-1024x538.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Jewish%20protester%20in%20a%20pro-Palestine%20demonstration%20in%20the%20US.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40jvplive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Hamas%20is%20raising%20its%20voice%20for%20their%20release.%20But%20its%20words%20are%20considered%20offensive%20since%20it%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20international%20community.%20But%20if%20no%20one%20else%20speaks%20for%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20then%20should%20the%20Palestinians%20not%20listen%20to%20Hamas%20just%20because%20it%20has%20been%20declared%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20powerful%20of%20the%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20whether%20the%20Palestinians%20will%20be%20released%20or%20not.%20Then%20why%20is%20Hamas%20ready%20for%20this%20ceasefire%3F%20Because%20it%20is%20important%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20to%20survive.%20It%20is%20necessary%20for%20them%20to%20get%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20access%20to%20internet.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20treat%20the%20injured%20Palestinians%20left%20behind%20among%20the%2013%2C000%20that%20are%20dead.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20people%20to%20get%20food%20and%20water.%20Every%20minute%20of%20absence%20of%20firing%20or%20bombing%20means%20a%20life%20saved%2C%20a%20limb%20still%20attached%20to%20the%20body%20it%20belongs%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20governments%20of%20the%20power%20wielding%20world%20would%20not%20allow%20it%20as%20they%20have%20closed%20ranks%20behind%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20against%20Hamas%20is%20that%20it%20was%20not%20concerned%20about%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20Why%20else%20would%20it%20have%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%3F%20Did%20it%20not%20know%20how%20Israel%20would%20react%3F%20I%20found%20this%20question%20very%20interesting.%20Implicit%20in%20this%20question%20is%20the%20assumption%20that%20Israel%20is%20a%20bully%20and%20you%20should%20not%20do%20anything%20even%20if%20it%20is%20beating%20you%20daily%2C%20looting%20your%20houses%20and%20land.%20And%20that%20you%20do%20not%20expect%20a%20measured%20response%20from%20it%20to%20any%20crisis.%20That%20it%20would%20indiscriminately%20wreak%20vengeance%20on%20everyone%20it%20thinks%20Hamas%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20if%20Hamas%20is%20ready%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20then%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20decision%20is%20its%20concern%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685321%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%2F%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20just%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20not%20only%20Israel%2C%20but%20also%20the%20governments%20of%20its%20patron%20states%20like%20the%20US%2C%20England%2C%20Canada%20and%20Germany%20were%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20stopping%20violence%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20Why%20are%20they%20now%20eager%20for%20it%3F%20They%20were%20after%20all%20not%20averse%20to%20killing%20children%2C%20attacking%20hospitals%20and%20UN%20facilities%2C%20destroying%20Gaza.%20Remember%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20callous%20response%C2%A0%20to%20the%20question%20about%20ceasefire%3F%20He%20had%20smugly%20responded%20%3A%20%E2%80%98No.%20Not%20possible.%E2%80%99%20So%20what%20has%20changed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20decision%20of%20ceasefire%20is%20taken%2C%20then%20its%20credit%20belongs%20to%20the%20American%20and%20European%20youth%20that%20has%20not%20left%20the%20streets%20since%20the%20Israeli%20attack%20and%20have%20continued%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20their%20governments%20to%20ask%20Israel%20to%20go%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Lakhs%20of%20youngsters%20%E2%80%93%20in%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Toronto%20and%20Berlin%2C%20and%20scores%20of%20other%20big%20and%20small%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20and%20other%20wester%20countries%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20carrying%20Palestinian%20flags%2C%20have%20been%20demonstrating%20against%20the%20Israeli%20attack.%20They%20are%20blocking%20railway%20stations%2C%20bridges%2C%20and%20intersections.%20Protesters%20took%20over%20the%20stage%20of%20a%20Democratic%20Party%20convention%20in%20the%20USA.%20They%20are%20protesting%20against%20their%20Democrat%20delegates%20for%20not%20advocating%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Same%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20England%20where%20the%20voters%20of%20the%20liberal%20Labour%20Party%20are%20protesting%20against%20their%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20worldwide%20revolt%20of%20the%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20young%2C%20against%20their%20governments%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20move%20towards%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125107%2F20231014_125837-copy.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125107%2F20231014_125837-copy.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125107%2F20231014_125837-copy-300x192.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680300%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAbout%20150%20citizens%20gathered%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20protest%20Israeli%20atrocities%20in%20Palestine.%20Photo%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20working%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20Israeli%20lobby%2C%20is%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20unpopular%20by%20each%20passing%20day%20because%20of%20its%20support%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20violence.%20Public%20opinion%20is%20growing%20against%20Biden%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20re-election%20in%20the%20next%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20international%20public%20opinion%20being%20in%20favour%20of%20justice%20for%20Palestine%2C%20it%20is%20now%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20Israel%20to%20continue%20its%20killing%20spree.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20in%20Israel%20itself%20are%20protesting%20against%20the%20government.%20Jews%20and%20Arabs%20together.%20A%20long%20march%20has%20just%20reached%20Jerusalem.%20Many%20Israeli%20women%20are%20saying%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20does%20not%20care%20about%20the%20Israelis%20arrested%20by%20Hamas.%20The%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20could%20put%20the%20hostages%20at%20risk%2C%20but%20the%20government%20is%20not%20even%20thinking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20and%20Netanyahu%20are%20rapidly%20losing%20public%20support%20within%20their%20country.%20Netanyahu%20also%20understands%20that%20the%20wave%20of%20sympathy%20that%20had%20arisen%20in%20favor%20of%20Israel%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20of%20October%207%2C%20is%20now%20turning%20against%20it%20after%20its%20brutal%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20and%20its%20sadistic%20destruction%20for%20the%20last%2044%20days.%20The%20images%20of%20murdered%2C%20limbless%20children%2C%20of%20little%20bodies%20packed%20in%20body%20bags%2C%20arouse%20repulsion%2C%20hatred%2C%20and%20anger%20against%20Israel.%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20till%20a%20day%20ago%20had%20balked%20at%20any%20proposal%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20is%20now%20under%20tremendous%20pressure%20from%20his%20patron%20governments%20as%20they%20fear%20that%20any%20delay%20will%20turn%20world%20opinion%20against%20them%20and%20Israel.%20But%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20tide%20has%20already%20turned%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11131313%2Fpalestine-support-e1697010347514.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11131313%2Fpalestine-support-e1697010347514.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11131313%2Fpalestine-support-e1697010347514-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11131313%2Fpalestine-support-e1697010347514-1024x512.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11131313%2Fpalestine-support-e1697010347514-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679453%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESupport%20for%20Palestine%20in%20Market%20Street%2C%20SF%2C%20CA.%20Photo%3A%20Tinou%20Bao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20impossible%20for%20the%20world%20to%20remain%20silent%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20violence%20after%20watching%20Gaza%20turning%20into%20rubble%2C%20children%20being%20shot%20directly%2C%20hospitals%20being%20bombed%20and%20ICU%20patients%20dying%20on%20TV.%20The%20world%20is%20speaking.%20As%20days%20pass%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20clear%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20intention%20is%20not%20to%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20Hamas%20but%20that%20it%20wants%20completely%20cleanse%20Gaza%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20capture%20it.%20This%20is%20an%20expansionist%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%20becoming%20impossible%20even%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20to%20justify%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20al-Shifa%20hospital%20by%20Israel.%20Israel%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20able%20to%20prove%20its%20claim%20that%20the%20hospital%20was%20the%20command%20and%20control%20centre%20of%20Hamas.%20The%20video%20evidence%20it%20has%20released%20to%20prove%20its%20claim%20is%20not%20trusted%20even%20by%20the%20media%20platforms%20sympathetic%20to%20it%2C%20such%20as%20BBC%20and%20New%20York%20Times%20or%20CNN.%20Even%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20digest%20the%20laughable%2C%20edited%20videos%20presented%20to%20them%20by%20Israel.%20They%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20say%20that%20till%20now%20Israel%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20present%20solid%20evidence%20that%20the%20hospital%20was%20being%20used%20by%20Hamas.%20Yet%20it%20has%20turned%20the%20hospital%20into%20debris.%20Not%20only%20al-Shifa%2C%20it%20has%20destroyed%20other%20hospitals%20as%20well.%20As%20I%20write%20this%2C%20the%20news%20is%20that%20Israel%20has%20bombed%20UN-run%20schools%20and%20killed%20more%20than%20200%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20searching%20for%20Hamas%20which%20%C2%A0is%20hiding%20among%20the%20civilians%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20hence%20it%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20kill%20them%20all%2C%20Israel%20is%20now%20saying%20that%20Hamas%20is%20in%20southern%20Gaza.%20Earlier%20Israel%20was%20asking%20Palestinians%20to%20move%20to%20South%20Gaza%20for%20safety.%20Now%20it%20is%20taking%20them%20to%20vacate%20it.%20Then%20where%20should%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20go%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685368%2Fanand-patwardhan-idfa-immediate-ceasefire%2F%5C%22%3EIn%20IDFA%20Award%20Acceptance%20Speech%2C%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20Calls%20For%20%E2%80%98Immediate%20Ceasefire%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Just%20Peace%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israel%20%C2%A0shamelessly%20says%20that%20it%20is%20not%20its%20problem.%20It%20just%20wants%20Gaza%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20parking%20lot%20free%20of%20its%20people.%20The%20way%20it%20is%20planting%20its%20flag%20on%20hospitals%20and%20cemeteries%2C%20and%20flattened%20land%2C%20on%20the%20hillocks%20of%20rubble%20and%20ruins%20of%20Gaza%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20it%20only%20wants%20to%20expand%20its%20territory.%20After%20watching%20all%20this%2C%20how%20can%20one%20continue%20its%20support%20to%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20Jews%20have%20joined%20protests%20against%20the%20violence%20of%20Israel.%20Their%20visible%20presence%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20dismiss%20all%20opposition%20by%20calling%20it%20anti-semitic.%20People%20hear%20the%20Israeli%20ministers%20and%20leaders%20when%20they%20say%20that%20they%20want%20all%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20be%20driven%20out%20of%20Gaza%20and%20not%20to%20return%20even%20after%20the%20war.%20Its%20leaders%20shamelessly%20ask%20as%20to%20why%20other%20countries%20cannot%20absorb%20them.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20world%20understand%20well%20the%20evil%20intent%20of%20Israel%20to%20eliminate%20Palestinians%20and%20have%20risen%20against%20it%20and%20their%20governments%20for%20their%20heartless%20support%20to%20the%20criminal%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20is%20neither%20the%20humanity%20of%20Biden%20or%20other%20prime%20ministers%20of%20the%20west%2C%20nor%20the%20kindness%20of%20Netanyahu%20that%20they%20are%20thinking%20of%20stopping%20the%20violence%20for%20five%20days.This%20is%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20save%20ground%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20be%20the%C2%A0%20reason%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20stop%20Israeli%20violence%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Why%20this%20is%20important%20can%20be%20understood%20today%20by%20reading%20a%20post%20by%20a%20Palestinian%3A%20%E2%80%9936%20people%20from%20my%20family%20were%20killed%20yesterday.%20If%20the%20war%20had%20stopped%20yesterday%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20alive.%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20the%20story%20of%20every%20family%20in%20Gaza.%20One%20in%20every%20200%20people%20has%20been%20killed.%20Every%20minute%20someone%20is%20being%20killed.%20A%20child%20is%20being%20murdered%20every%2010%20minutes.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20carry%20on%20the%20business%20of%20the%20world%20with%20the%20burden%20of%20this%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700537411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28154925%2Fimage-1445.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsympathy-for-israel-has-evaporated-all-eyes-are-on-ceasefire-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20people%20of%20the%20world%20understand%20well%20the%20evil%20intent%20of%20Israel%20to%20eliminate%20Palestinians%20and%20have%20risen%20against%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsympathy-for-israel-has-evaporated-all-eyes-are-on-ceasefire-now%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22