Jillette%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20performing%20duo%20Penn%20And%20Teller.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700535420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fd5p361us_shefalishah_120x90_21_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Finternational-emmys-2023-no-win-for-best-actress-nominee-shefali-shah-4591054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Emmys%20went%20to%20Mexican%20actress%20Karla%20Souza%20and%20UK%20star%20Martin%20Freeman%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Finternational-emmys-2023-no-win-for-best-actress-nominee-shefali-shah-4591054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Finternational-emmys-2023-no-win-for-best-actress-nominee-shefali-shah-4591054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Finternational-emmys-2023-no-win-for-best-actress-nominee-shefali-shah-4591054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Arrests%20NBC%20Journalist%20For%20Inciting%20Terror%2C%20Glorifying%20Hamas%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENBC%20News%20has%20cut%20ties%20with%20a%C2%A0Palestinian%20journalist%20after%20she%20was%20arrested%20by%20Israeli%20authorities%20Thursday%20for%20glorifying%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%C2%A0According%20to%20th%3Cem%3Ee%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fcrime-in-israel%2Farticle-773968%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fcrime-in-israel%2Farticle-773968%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJerusalem%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mirvat%20al-Azzeh%2C%C2%A0a%2045-year-old%20freelance%20producer%2C%20was%20booked%20on%20suspicion%20of%20inciting%20terrorism%20and%20identifying%20with%20a%20terrorist%20organization%C2%A0after%20sharing%20four%20posts%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''These%20are%20very%20serious%20offenses%20during%20a%20time%20of%20declared%20war%20when%20the%20respondent%20lives%20and%20makes%20a%20living%20in%20the%20same%20country%20that%20is%20under%20attack%20and%20yet%20chooses%20to%20incite%20and%20glorify%20the%20horrible%20acts%20committed%20against%20civilians%2C''%20a%20police%20spokesperson%20stated%20in%20court%2C%20as%20per%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Fbusiness%2Fisrael-arrests-nbc-journalist-for-glorifying-hamas-attacks%2F%5C%22%3E%20New%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2Cal-Azzeh%C2%A0wrote%20on%20Facebook%20about%20an%20elderly%20woman%20who%20was%20kidnapped%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20killing%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20black%20comedy%2C%20the%20old%20woman%20looks%20happy%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20action%20before%20she%20dies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20in%20another%2C%20''Sirens%20all%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Jews%20are%20hiding%20and%20the%20Arabs%20are%20out%20drinking%20coffee%20on%20their%20balconies.''%20She%20also%20said%20she%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20''watching%20a%20movie%20where%20the%20director%20is%20Palestinian%20and%20the%20protagonists%20are%20from%20Gaza.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20representative%20at%20a%20Friday%20hearing%20of%20the%20Jerusalem%20Magistrate's%20Court%20claimed%20that%20she%20chose%20%26quot%3Bto%20incite%20and%20glorify%20the%20horrible%20acts%20committed%20against%20civilians.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20defense%20attorney%20said%20that%20al-Azzeh%C2%A0confirmed%20that%20the%20posts%20were%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20a%20normative%20woman%2C%20engaged%20in%20journalism%2C%20and%20her%20role%20is%20very%20important%20to%20everyone.%20She%20was%20asked%20in%20her%20investigation%20about%20her%20work.%20I%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20things%20attributed%20to%20her%2C%20she%20cooperated%20fully.%20She%20did%20not%20try%20to%20hide%2C%20saying%20'I%20had%20a%20hacker%2C''%20her%20defense%20attorney%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20believe%20she%20admitted%20to%20all%20the%20deeds%20described%20to%20her%20and%20cooperated%20fully%20with%20the%20investigation.%20She%20did%20not%20attempt%20to%20conceal%20the%20offenses%20or%20claim%20that%20her%20accounts%20had%20been%20hacked.%20Even%20when%20she%20didn't%20have%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20which%20is%20the%20main%20tool%20involved%2C%20she%20still%20said%2C%20'Yes%2C%20those%20are%20my%20posts.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20NBC%20News%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20has%20severed%20ties%20with%20her%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20began%20working%20for%20the%20network%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fnbc-cuts-ties-palestinian-journalist-arrested-israel-inciting-terrorism-social-media%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''The%20investigation%20of%20Ms.%20Azza%20is%20unrelated%20to%20NBC%20News.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20her%20personal%20Facebook%20posts%20that%20predate%20her%20time%20with%20us%20as%20a%20freelancer.%20We%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20those%20posts%20before%20we%20engaged%20Ms.%20Azza%20four%20weeks%20ago.%20She%20will%20not%20be%20contributing%20to%20our%20coverage%20going%20forward.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20al-Azzeh's%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20she%20has%20been%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20since%20September%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war%20triggered%20by%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20have%20carried%20out%20large-scale%20arrests%20of%20Palestinians%20suspected%20of%20links%20to%20Hamas%20or%20of%20inciting%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700535360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fatjeem_mirvat-alazzeh_625x300_21_November_23.jpeg