)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46-300x191.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46-1024x650.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESinghbhum%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20grow%20hundreds%20of%20nutritious%20folk%20varieties%20of%20rice%2C%20but%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20have%20switched%20to%20cultivating%20other%20varieties.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20new%20strategy%20to%20combat%20anaemia%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20October%202021%2C%20it%20began%20supplying%20new%20kind%20of%20rice%2C%20chemically%20fortified%20with%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B12%20and%20folic%20acid%2C%20to%20the%20poor%20here%2C%20including%20small%20farmers%20such%20as%20Kamal%20Kant%20Gope%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Panajea%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndustrial%20processing%2C%20and%20abrasive%20polishing%20to%20increase%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwhiteness%E2%80%9D%20of%20rice%20strips%20the%20grain%20of%20its%20bran%20layer%2C%20a%20dietary%20fibre%20rich%20in%20minerals%20and%20other%20nutrients.%20As%20rice%20grains%20get%20stripped%20of%20nutrients%2C%20some%20development%20experts%20advocate%20re-introducing%20nutrients%20into%20rice%2C%20by%20fortifying%20it%20with%20a%20micronutrient%20premix.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20policy%20called%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20scale%20fortification%E2%80%9D%2C%20micro-nutrients%20are%20artificially%20added%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3Estaples%2C%20such%20as%20rice.%20How%20it%20is%20being%20done%20in%20rice%20is%20this%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dried%20powder%20%E2%80%9Cpre-mix%E2%80%9D%20of%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20%E2%80%93%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B12%2C%20folic%20acid%20%E2%80%93%20is%20added%20into%20broken%20rice%2C%20or%20powdered%20rice%20grains.%20The%20paste%2C%20containing%20factory-made%20nutrients%2C%20is%20passed%20through%20pasta-extrusion%20equipment%20to%20manufacture%20new%20grains%2C%20with%20a%20slightly%20artificial%20appearance%20compared%20to%20natural%20rice.%20The%20new%20grains%20are%20mixed%20into%20regular%20rice%20supplied%20to%20the%20poor%20monthly%20in%20gunny%20bags%20as%20a%20food%20subsidy%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDalbhumgarh%20and%20Chakulia%20blocks%20were%20among%20the%20sites%20in%20a%20national%20pilot%20study%20for%20this%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20scheme%2C%20chosen%20because%20most%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20rice%20mills%20are%20located%20here%2C%20and%20also%20because%20of%20the%20history%20and%20trend%20of%20paddy%20production%20here.%20It%20has%20now%20been%20many%20months%20since%20Gope%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Dalbhumgarh%2C%20first%20held%20a%20new%20opaque%20rice%20grain%20made%20in%20an%20industrial%20unit%20in%20his%20palm%2C%20instead%20of%20translucent%20grains%20that%20ripen%20every%20year%20in%20the%20emerald%20stalks%20in%20his%20fields.%20He%20remained%20sceptical%20of%20what%20the%20government%20was%20providing%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfood%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20pressures%20us%20to%20eat%20it%20saying%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9CVitamin%20Rice%E2%80%9D%2C%20at%20least%20it%20ought%20to%20have%20some%20taste%20or%20the%20qualities%20of%20rice%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gope%20asked.%20He%20explained%20with%20some%20exasperation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20rice.%20If%20I%20hold%20it%20tight%20in%20my%20fist%2C%20it%20falls%20away%20like%20a%20grain%20of%20sand%2C%20it%20does%20not%20stick%20like%20rice.%20Even%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20water%20left%20after%20rice%20is%20cooked)%20is%20of%20very%20thin%20consistency.%20Then%20how%20can%20it%20be%20nutritious%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat-1024x769.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20fortified%20rice%20made%20using%20extrusion%20machine%20in%20a%20factory%20have%20an%20artificial%20appearance%20compared%20to%20natural%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGope%20said%20that%20those%20who%20cultivate%20rice%20such%20as%20him%20know%20what%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20food%E2%80%9D%20is.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20village%2C%20we%20have%20eaten%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edheki%20ka%20chaawal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20pound%20and%20mill%20paddy%20into%20rice%20ourselves%20at%20home%2C%20in%20small%20batches.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5Bstarch%5D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20that%20rice%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eis%20so%20thick%2C%20it%20contains%20nutrients%20from%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLocally%2C%20we%20have%20paddy%20varieties%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMakarkanthi%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaankri%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENohaachi-dhaan%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENohaachi-dhaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20thick%20bran%20is%20red%2C%20almost%20black%2C%20in%20colour%20with%20grains%20filled%20with%20nutrients.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20delicious%20%E2%80%93%20thicker%20than%20milk%20with%20Horlicks!%20Yet%2C%20the%20local%20rice%20is%20light%20and%20easy%20to%20digest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGope%20who%20is%20the%20traditional%20headman%20of%20his%20village%20Panajea%2C%20was%20not%20only%20unconvinced%20by%20the%20government%20policy%20on%20rice%20fortification%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20also%20alarmed%20and%20anxious.%20He%20believed%20that%20the%20new%20fortified%20grains%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20those%20who%20are%20not%20well.%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%2C%20not%20everyone%20will%20be%20able%20to%20digest%20this%20new%20rice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20since%20this%20rice%20started%20being%20distributed%2C%20we%20have%20had%20two%20instances%20where%20people%20who%20fell%20ill%20needed%20blood%20transfusions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20rice%20has%20additional%20vitamins%2C%20then%20why%20is%20that%20happening%3F%20How%20do%20we%20know%20if%20it%20is%20even%20helping%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAt%20risk%20and%20uncertain%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInside%20Panajea%20village%2C%20this%20reporter%20met%20one%20of%20the%20individuals%20whose%20health%20Gope%20was%20concerned%20about.%20Rahul%20Gope%2C%20a%20quiet%20teenager%20dressed%20in%20a%20t-shirt%20and%20shorts%2C%20had%20a%20slight%20build%2C%20which%20made%20him%20appear%20smaller%20than%20his%20age.%20His%20face%20was%20pale%20and%20his%20eyes%20had%20turned%20yellow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Chherani%20Gope%20shared%20multiple%20laboratory%20reports%20that%20showed%20how%20Rahul%20had%20undergone%20two%20blood%20transfusions%20in%20the%20previous%20three%20weeks%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20life%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20first%20blood%20transfusion%2C%20laboratory%20reports%20showed%2C%20he%20had%20a%20blood%20haemoglobin%20level%20%E2%80%93%20an%20essential%20protein%20carrying%20oxygen%20in%20the%20body%20%E2%80%93%20of%20merely%205.9.%20This%20was%20not%20even%20half%20of%20the%20healthy%20norm%20for%20his%20age.%20He%20was%20severely%20anaemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reports%20also%20showed%20excess%20bilirubin%2C%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20normal%2C%20showing%20an%20excess%20in%20his%20body%20of%20a%20pigment%20formed%20from%20a%20breakdown%20of%20blood%20cells.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Chherani%20Gope%20shared%20medical%20reports%20that%20showed%20no%20clear%20diagnosis%20of%20his%20severe%20anaemia%2C%20accompanied%20with%20jaundice.%20Photos%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20family%20said%20they%20had%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%2020%2C000%20on%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20nearest%20health%20facility%20and%20laboratory%2C%2040%20km%20away%20in%20Jhargram%20in%20Bengal%20(the%20neighbouring%20state)%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20have%20a%20diagnosis%20for%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20condition.%20They%20live%20more%20than%20100%20km%20away%20from%20Jamshedpur%20city%2C%20where%20tertiary%20health%20facilities%20are%20located.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20in%20public%20schemes%20is%20a%20response%20to%20chronically%20high%20levels%20of%20anaemia%20in%20the%20Indian%20population%2C%20which%20manifests%2C%20among%20other%20forms%2C%20in%20low%20haemoglobin%20levels%20such%20as%20Rahul%E2%80%99s.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20government%20acknowledges%20that%20it%20could%20potentially%20harm%20those%20like%20him%2C%20whose%20low%20haemoglobin%20could%20be%20a%20result%20of%20other%20conditions%20such%20as%20inherited%20blood%20disorders%20prevalent%20in%20this%20region%E2%80%99s%20Adivasi%20residents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20these%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fsickle-cell-disease%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esickle%20cell%20disease%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20blood%20disorder%20caused%20by%20a%20genetic%20mutation.%20In%20it%2C%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20blood%20cells%20are%20misshapen%2C%20like%20sickles%20or%20crescents.%20Such%20misshapen%20cells%20can%20get%20stuck%20in%20blood%20vessels%2C%20causing%20organ%20damage%2C%20debilitating%20pain%2C%20and%20strokes.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20largely%20affects%20Adivasi%20communities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fthalassemias%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThalassemia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20another%20inherited%20blood%20disorder%20caused%20by%20damaged%20or%20missing%20genes%20in%20which%20the%20body%20does%20not%20make%20adequate%20haemoglobin.%20It%20is%20managed%20with%20regular%20blood%20transfusions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22903%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1.jpeg%20903w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1-300x266.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIn%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%2C%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20misshapen%20blood%20cells%20look%20like%20sickles%2C%20and%20can%20block%20the%20major%20blood%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20each%20gunny%20bag%20containing%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20carries%20a%20warning%20in%20small%20print%20in%20English%20%E2%80%93%20a%20language%20neither%20understood%20nor%20spoken%20by%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20poor%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20fortified%20rice%20is%20not%20meant%20for%20those%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20and%20thalassemia.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20effect%20of%20additional%20iron%20stores%20from%20iron%20fortified%20food%20is%20not%20clear%20or%20known%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0002916523233171%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuch%20individuals%E2%80%99%20bodies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20the%20excess%20iron%20gets%20stored%2C%20it%20may%20potentially%20damage%20their%20organs%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Frice-fortification-programme-iron-anaemia-7470938%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esay%20experts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20symptoms%20Rahul%20was%20suffering%20from%20%E2%80%93%20very%20low%20haemoglobin%20combined%20with%20jaundice%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20seen%20in%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20disease.%20But%20that%20afternoon%2C%20Rahul%20had%20neither%20any%20information%20nor%20access%20to%20tests%20to%20determine%20whether%20he%20was%20among%20those%20who%20ought%20to%20avoid%20eating%20the%20iron%20fortified%20rice.%20Nor%20was%20any%20alternate%20food%20provided%20to%20him%20in%20the%20public%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Diktat%E2%80%99%20to%20feed%20fortified%20rice%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficials%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Ranchi%2C%20180%20km%20away%2C%20who%20run%20the%20scheme%20to%20distribute%20ration%20rice%2C%20said%20they%20lack%20information%20on%20how%20many%20of%20existing%20food%20rations%20card%20holders%20in%20Jharkhand%20already%20suffer%20from%20such%20%E2%80%9Chemoglobinopathies%E2%80%9D%2C%20disorders%20such%20as%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20or%20thalassemia%2C%20and%20are%20thus%20supposed%20to%20avoid%20eating%20the%20iron-fortified%20rice.%20Nor%20did%20the%20department%20have%20provisions%20to%20give%20them%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20chemically%20fortified%20rice%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20continuing%20to%20provide%20them%20custom%20milled%20rice%20as%20it%20did%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20positive%20thing%20is%20that%20since%20the%20distribution%20of%20iron-fortified%20rice%20began%2C%20we%20have%20not%20got%20an%20adverse%20health%20report%20from%20the%20field%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%2C%20overseeing%20the%20new%20policy%E2%80%99s%20implementation%2C%20stated%20about%20his%20discomfort%20with%20the%20scheme.%20He%20added%20that%20when%20several%20critics%2C%20including%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20former%20minister%20for%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20Sarayu%20Roy%2C%20publicly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flagatar24.com%2Fformer-food-and-civil-supply-minister-saryu-roy-raises-doubt-on-quality-of-fortified-rice-distributed-under-pds%2F91094%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20scheme%2C%20to%20improve%20public%20understanding%2C%20the%20department%20had%20organised%20workshops%2C%20inviting%20medical%20experts%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20organisations%20who%20work%20on%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20and%20civil%20society%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%B