%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%99%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%9A%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%3A%20%7C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B7%E0%A5%81%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%3A%20%7C%7C%2018%7C%7C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinded%20by%20egotism%2C%20strength%2C%20arrogance%2C%20desire%2C%20and%20anger%2C%20the%20vile%20men%20abuse%20Me%2C%20who%20am%20present%20in%20their%20own%20body%20and%20in%20the%20bodies%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20assume%20here%20that%20%E2%80%9CMe%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20last%20verse%20refers%20not%20to%20God%2C%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Being%2C%20but%20to%20Cricket%2C%20our%20most%20beloved%20game%20(and%20secular%20national%20religion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20as%20a%20man%20in%20his%20seventh%20decade%20of%20life%20%E2%80%93%20who%20watched%20his%20first%20Test%20match%2C%20at%20age%207%2C%20in%201969%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20remarkable%20thing%20about%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20final%20was%20that%20so%20many%20neutrals%20everywhere%20(by%20which%20I%20mean%20cricket%20fans%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20Indian%20or%20Australian)%20were%20cheering%20not%20for%20India%20but%20for%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20because%20India%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20underdogs%20in%20the%20final%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20why%20neutrals%20don%E2%80%99t%20back%20a%20particular%20competitor.%20But%20being%20better%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20put%20neutrals%20off.%20Few%20non-Englishmen%20cheered%20for%20England%20in%20the%201979%20final%2C%20preferring%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20then%20favoured%20so%20heavily%20to%20win%20that%20their%20losing%20would%20have%20been%20a%20cosmic%20shock%20(as%20it%20was%20in%201983%2C%20when%20they%20lost%20to%20India%2C%20back%20then%20a%20kinder%20country%20than%20it%20is%20now%2C%20more%20self-effacing%2C%20less%20triumphalist%20and%20ugly).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeutrals%20cheered%20Australia%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20team%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20unloved%20outside%20its%20own%20shores%2C%20because%20most%20cricket%20fans%20worldwide%20are%20thoroughly%20sick%20%E2%80%93%20fed%20up%2C%20pissed%20off%20%E2%80%93%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20bully-boy%20dominance%20of%20world%20cricket.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20sporting%20dominance%2C%20which%20neutral%20fans%20can%20live%20with%20(as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20West%20Indians%20of%20the%20Clive%20Lloyd%20and%20Viv%20Richards%20era%2C%20or%20Brazilian%20football%20in%20the%20time%20of%20Pel%C3%A9).%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20wholesale%20takeover%20by%20the%20BCCI%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20financing%2C%20values%2C%20and%20calendar%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20grip%20over%20the%20game%20that%20is%20stronger%2C%20more%20ruthless%20and%20vice-like%2C%20more%20absolute%20and%20remorseless%2C%20more%20self-serving%20and%20mercantilist%2C%20than%20that%20once%20exercised%20by%20the%20game%E2%80%99s%20original%20overlords%20in%20England%20(who%20might%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20have%20been%20forgiven%20their%20assertion%20of%20ownership%20over%20cricket%20because%20they%20did%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20give%20us%20the%20game).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20has%20warped%20cricket%2C%20distorted%20it%2C%20making%20it%20so%20India-centric%20that%20other%20proud%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20some%20with%20better%20pedigrees%20than%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20bit-part%20players%2C%20mendicants%2C%20petitioners%20for%20match-time.%20Everything%20is%20now%20about%20India%3A%20the%20crowds%2C%20the%20songs%2C%20the%20scheduling%2C%20the%20pitches%2C%20the%20money.%20The%20one%20element%20the%20BCCI%20cannot%20control%2C%20mercifully%2C%20is%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20match.%20Try%20as%20the%20BJP%20might%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20BCCI%20is%20now%20the%20BJP%20in%20cricketing%20form%20%E2%80%93%20the%20result%20of%20a%20match%20cannot%20be%20influenced%20to%20suit%20its%20needs%20the%20way%20an%20election%20can.%20International%20umpires%20are%20not%20the%20Indian%20judiciary.%20The%20ICC%20is%20not%20(yet)%20the%20Indian%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20India%20lost%20in%20the%20final%20was%20karmic%20payback%20for%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20sins%20against%20the%20game%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20be%20sporting%20and%20civilised%2C%20to%20appreciate%20cricket%20as%20something%20other%20than%20a%20jingoistic%20exercise%20in%20which%20India%20must%20win%20every%20game%20to%20the%20chanting%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%E2%80%9D.%20Let%20us%20never%20again%20hold%20the%20final%20of%20a%20World%20Cup%20in%20such%20a%20city%2C%20a%20place%20in%20which%20cricket%20is%20but%20the%20means%20to%20petty%20nationalist%20ends%2C%20where%20few%20stand%20up%20to%20applaud%20an%20opposing%20batsman%20who%20scores%20a%20magnificent%2C%20match-winning%20hundred.%20Stay%20with%20Chennai%2C%20with%20Mumbai%2C%20with%20Kolkata%2C%20where%20the%20crowds%20love%20cricket%20(and%20not%20just%20winning).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%5C%22%3EHush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20justice%20was%20done.%20Australia%20won.%20Narendra%20Modi%20did%20not%20get%20his%20heavily%20scripted%20opportunity%20to%20strut%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20stadium%20named%20after%20him.%20Instead%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20most%20graceless%20presentation%20of%20a%20cup%20to%20a%20winning%20captain%2C%20in%20which%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20sulking%20like%20a%20spoiled%20child%20who%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20celebration%20he%E2%80%99d%20thought%20was%20his%20birthright%20%E2%80%93%20handed%20over%20the%20trophy%20to%20Pat%20Cummins%20and%20then%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20the%20Australian%20captain.%20The%20latter%20was%20left%20bemused%20and%20sheepish%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20alone%20with%20the%20cup%20that%20his%20team%20had%20won%20but%20feeling%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20like%20a%20gate-crasher%20at%20a%20party-gone-wrong.%20For%20India%2C%20it%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20national%20embarrassment.%20The%20prime%20minister%20had%20reduced%20an%20ancient%20land%20to%20a%20boorish%20place%2C%20ill-mannered%2C%20inhospitable%2C%20uncivilised%2C%20nouveau-riche.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20give%20thanks%20to%20the%20God%20of%20Cricket%20that%20the%20BCCI%20lost%20on%20Sunday%2C%20even%20as%20we%20embrace%20our%20gallant%20boys%20in%20blue.%20Maybe%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20emboldened%20now%20to%20push%20back%20against%20the%20BCCI%20in%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeat%20after%20me%3A%20Cricket%20Mata%20ki%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETunku%20Varadarajan%20is%20a%20writer%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3Cem%3E%20in%20New%20York.%20A%20fellow%20at%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20he%20is%20also%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Classical%20Liberal%20Institute%20at%20New%20York%20University%20Law%20School.%20He%20has%20written%20frequently%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3EWisden%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700532043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20234455%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-11.44.17-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad-on-sunday%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20India%20lost%20in%20the%20final%20was%20karmic%20payback%20for%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20sins%20against%20the%20game%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20be%20sporting%20and%20civilised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad-on-sunday%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20New%20CEO%20Spent%20Decade%20Trying%20To%20Tackle%20Abuse%2C%20Racism%20At%20Twitch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEmmett%20Shear%2C%20OpenAI's%20interim%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20led%20the%20Twitch%20livestreaming%20site%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20building%20a%20burgeoning%20business%2C%20but%20he%20struggled%20to%20keep%20misogynists%2C%20racists%20and%20even%20pedophiles%20from%20running%20rampant%20on%20the%20video%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20computer%20scientist%20helped%20transform%20a%20niche%20video-game%20streaming%20company%20into%20an%20entertainment%20giant%20-%20one%20that%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20purchased%20for%20%24970%20million%20in%202014.%20From%20former%20executives%2C%20he%20gets%20high%20marks%20for%20his%20focus%20on%20growth%2C%20making%20Twitch%20the%20go-to%20service%20for%20livestreaming%20and%20gaming%20culture%2C%20and%20for%20ferreting%20out%20some%20of%20the%20abuses%20at%20an%20internet%20business%20built%20on%20user-generated%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Emmett%20Shear%20needs%20to%20quell%20an%20open%20revolt%20among%20OpenAI%20employees.%20After%20his%20appointment%2C%20nearly%20all%20threatened%20to%20quit%20unless%20the%20board%20resigned%2C%20and%20both%20Microsoft%20Corp.%20and%20Salesforce%20Inc.%20have%20tried%20to%20poach%20its%20talent.%20At%20Twitch%2C%20Shear%20left%20a%20controversial%20legacy.%20While%20few%20doubted%20his%20technical%20abilities%2C%20he%20drew%20criticism%20for%20coarse%20comments%20and%20for%20scandals%20during%20his%20stewardship.%20He%20has%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20effective%20altruism%20movement%2C%20whose%20proponents%20played%20a%20central%20role%20in%20firing%20of%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwitch%20is%20still%20at%20times%20an%20outlet%20for%20extremist%20views%20and%20even%20a%20haven%20for%20child%20predators.%20As%20interim%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20Shear%20is%20at%20a%20similar%20juncture%20-%20being%20asked%20to%20balance%20breakneck%20growth%20while%20grappling%20with%20the%20ethical%20considerations%20that%20surround%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Thanks%20to%20social-media%20posts%2C%20some%20of%20his%20opinions%20on%20AI%20are%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20a%20safe%20AI%20without%20experimenting%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20experiment%20without%20progress%2C%20but%20we%20probably%20shouldn't%20be%20barreling%20ahead%20at%20max%20speed%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20Shear%20said%20in%20September%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20has%20praised%20AI's%20ability%20to%20solve%20problems%20involving%20chip%20design%2C%20material%20sciences%2C%20programming%20and%20electricity%20generation.%20He's%20even%20suggested%20AI%20could%20take%20over%20much%20of%20the%20work%20done%20in%20a%20company's%20C-suite.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20CEO%20job%20(and%20the%20majority%20of%20most%20executive%20jobs)%20are%20very%20automatable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Twitch%20executives%2C%20including%20some%20who%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20Shear's%20ability%20to%20lead%20OpenAI%20while%20acknowledging%20that%20few%20executives%20are%20fully%20equipped%20to%20step%20into%20such%20a%20tumultuous%20situation.%20None%20were%20surprised%20by%20the%20choice%2C%20citing%20Shear's%20technical%20expertise%20and%20curiosity%2C%20along%20with%20his%20success%20in%20building%20Twitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20several%20executives%20departed%20Twitch%20amid%20concerns%20that%20the%20platform%20had%20lost%20touch%20with%20its%20creators.%20Shear%20himself%20left%20in%20March%20of%20this%20year%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20his%20new%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20his%20years%20at%20Twitch%2C%20Shear%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20company's%20product%20team%20to%20continually%20improve%20the%20site's%20systems.%20An%20engineer%20by%20trade%2C%20he%20was%20still%20producing%20code%20as%20CEO%2C%20according%20to%20one%20former%20employee.%20They%20joke%20that%20the%20last%20of%20his%20work%20was%20running%20the%20TV%20in%20Twitch's%20lobby.%20People%20who%20worked%20with%20Shear%20describe%20him%20as%20deeply%20curious%20and%20a%20voracious%20reader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShear%20has%20ties%20to%20the%20effective%20altruism%20movement%2C%20which%20expresses%20reservations%20about%20advanced%20AI.%20Some%20people%20affiliated%20with%20the%20movement%20have%20imagined%20scenarios%20in%20which%20a%20powerful%20AI%20system%20could%20wreak%20widespread%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20credit%20Twitch's%20success%20with%20Shear's%20early%20decision%20to%20build%20its%20own%20content%20distribution%20network%20-%20its%20own%20interconnected%20servers.%20The%20network%20facilitated%20low-latency%20streaming%2C%20eliminating%20the%20buffering%20and%20interruptions%20that%20anger%20users.%20Competitors%2C%20using%20leased%20infrastructure%2C%20fell%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20cost%20of%20streaming%20was%20a%20third%20or%20quarter%20of%20what%20theirs%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Shear%20said%20at%20Twitch's%20annual%20convention%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20in%20October.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20done%20the%20very%20difficult%20work%20of%20building%20our%20own%20in-house%20backend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShear%2C%20who%20co-founded%20Twitch%20predecessor%20Justin.tv%2C%20credits%20Twitch's%20growth%20to%20his%20early%20recognition%20that%20gaming%20fans%20like%20himself%20would%20eagerly%20watch%20others%20play%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Twitch%20thing%20was%20because%20I%20really%2C%20really%2C%20really%2C%20really%20love%20Starcraft%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20TwitchCon%20of%20Activision%20Blizzard's%20highly%20competitive%20strategy%20game.%20%26quot%3BAlmost%20no%20one%20was%20streaming%20gaming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwitch's%20success%20at%20turning%20video%20gaming%20into%20a%20spectator%20sport%20helped%20birth%20the%20%24250%20billion%20creator%20economy%20-%20allowing%20social-media%20personalities%20to%20become%20the%20internet%20equivalent%20of%20Hollywood%20stars%2C%20endorsing%20products%20and%20attracting%20advertisers.%20The%20company%20later%20added%20the%20ability%20to%20donate%20money%20to%20streamers%20and%20subscribe%20to%20them.%20The%20payment%20infrastructure%20helped%20create%20gaming%20celebrities%20such%20as%20Tyler%20%26quot%3BNinja%26quot%3B%20Blevins%2C%20who%20earned%20millions%20playing%20Fortnite.%20Most%20of%20Twitch's%20content%20today%20falls%20into%20its%20%26quot%3BJust%20Chatting%26quot%3B%20category%2C%20not%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20former%20employees%20praise%20Shear's%20abilities%20as%20a%20technical%20leader%2C%20many%20question%20his%20people%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20people%20CEO%2C%20but%20he%20is%20a%20great%20tech%20CEO%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marcus%20Graham%2C%20a%20gaming%20executive%20who%20worked%20at%20Twitch%20from%202011%20to%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Twitch%20was%20considered%20a%20cesspool%20of%20misogyny%20and%20racism%2C%20where%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color%20male%20were%20regularly%20subjected%20to%20verbal%20abuse.%20In%202016%2C%20Shear%20introduced%20a%20machine%20learning%20feature%20called%20AutoMod%20that%20dramatically%20cut%20such%20comments.%20Moderators%20more%20consistently%20banned%20livestreamers%20who%20made%20hateful%20comments%2C%20including%20sexist%20rants.%20After%20several%20streamers%20were%20called%20out%20for%20abusive%20behavior%20in%202020%2C%20Shear%20sent%20a%20memo%20to%20staff%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20status%20quo%20needs%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%20has%20strict%20policies%20against%20such%20behavior%2C%20some%20problems%20remain.%20Child%20predators%20systematically%20find%20and%20attempt%20to%20groom%20users%20who%20appear%20to%20be%20under%2013%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20has%20reported.%20In%20July%202022%2C%20alleged%20predators%20found%20an%20average%20of%20673%20children%20on%20Twitch%20every%20day%2C%20according%20to%20a%20researcher.%20The%202022%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Black%20shoppers%20at%20a%20supermarket%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20New%20York%2C%20was%20broadcast%20live%20on%20Twitch%20for%20several%20minutes%20before%20being%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%202020%20report%20from%20GamesIndustry.Biz%20described%20sexist%20and%20boys-club%20attitudes%20internally%20at%20Twitch.%20Shear%20himself%20has%20made%20several%20controversial%20comments%20on%20X%2C%20including%20one%20remark%20about%20women%2C%20sex%20and%20bondage%2C%20that%20at%20the%20very%20least%20seemed%20inappropriate%20for%20a%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20described%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20opinionated%26quot%3B%20on%20X%2C%20Shear%20wasn't%20an%20outspoken%20presence%20as%20Twitch's%20leader.%20He%20rarely%20gave%20interviews%2C%20and%20internally%20at%20Twitch%2C%20Shear%20was%20known%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20product%20rather%20than%20company%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20my%20more%20difficult%20conversations%20with%20Emmett%20were%20the%20heart%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700531460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Foffpisco_emmett-shear_625x300_21_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmett-shear-sam-altman-openais-new-ceo-spent-decade-trying-to-tackle-abuse-racism-at-twitch-4591052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emmett%20Shear%2C%20OpenAI's%20interim%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20led%20the%20Twitch%20livestreaming%20site%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20building%20a%20burgeoning%20business%2C%20but%20he%20struggled%20to%20keep%20misogynists%2C%20racists%20and%20even%20pedophiles%20from%20running%20rampant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmett-shear-sam-altman-openais-new-ceo-spent-decade-trying-to-tackle-abuse-racism-at-twitch-4591052%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmett-shear-sam-altman-openais-new-ceo-spent-decade-trying-to-tackle-abuse-racism-at-twitch-4591052%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmett-shear-sam-altman-openais-new-ceo-spent-decade-trying-to-tackle-abuse-racism-at-twitch-4591052%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20%E2%80%98Scott%20Pilgrim%20Takes%20Off%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Makers%20and%20Stars%20Explain%20Their%20%E2%80%98Alternate-Reality%20Sequel%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20Why%20They%20Kept%20It%20a%20Secret%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700531433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F