nity%20succumbed%20to%20bullet%20injuries%20in%20the%20fresh%20violence%20that%20transpired%20on%20Monday%20(November%2020).%20The%20deceased%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Henminlen%20Vaiphei%2C%20son%20of%20Luntinlal%20Vaiphei%2C%20and%20Thangminlun%20Hangshing%2C%20son%20of%20Lunkhongam%20Hangshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%20issued%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20media%2C%20revealing%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20in%20the%20Kangchup%20area.%20Kuki-Zo%20village%20volunteers%2C%20patrolling%20the%20road%20between%20Leilon%20Vaiphei%20village%20and%20Kharam%20Vaiphei%20village%2C%20were%20allegedly%20ambushed%20by%20Meitei%20insurgents%20wearing%20state%20commandos%E2%80%99%20uniforms.%20This%20case%20bears%20resemblance%20to%20a%20previous%20ambush%20in%20the%20Kangchup%20area%2C%20where%20three%20volunteers%20were%20killed%20allegedly%20by%20disguised%20Meitei%20militants%20on%20September%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20escalating%20violence%2C%20COTU%20called%20for%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20on%20Monday%2C%20advocating%20for%20a%20shutdown%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district.%20According%20to%20COTU%2C%20the%20group%20responsible%20for%20the%20killings%20is%20the%20same%20group%20of%20disguised%20insurgents%20operating%20in%20Moreh%2C%20a%20border%20town%20in%20Tengnoupal%20district.%20COTU%20reported%20various%20alleged%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20this%20group%2C%20including%20looting%20church%20funds%2C%20burning%20vehicles%2C%20harassing%20women%20and%20children%2C%20and%20demolishing%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20police%20officer%20overseeing%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20helipad%20in%20Moreh%20was%20shot%20dead%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2031%2C%20by%20suspected%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20said%20that%20the%20deceased%20killed%20in%20the%20recent%20violence%20were%20repairing%20the%20Lamka-Kangpokpi%20road%2C%20damaged%20by%20the%20recent%20spell%20of%20rainfall.%20After%20dropping%20off%20their%20friends%20at%20a%20designated%20point%2C%20they%20were%20ambushed%20while%20attempting%20to%20return%20to%20Leimakhong%2C%20a%20mere%2050%20metres%20from%20where%20they%20left%20their%20friends.%20Since%20the%20victims%20and%20their%20friends%20were%20unarmed%2C%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20defend%20themselves.%20One%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%20Henminlen%20Vaiphei%2C%20served%20as%20personnel%20of%206th%20IRB%2C%20posted%20at%20Leimakhong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%2C%20it%20was%20observed%20that%20the%20roads%20were%20being%20repaired%20solely%20by%20the%20tribal%20community.%20With%20more%20than%20200%20deaths%20since%20May%203%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20promised%20in%20June%20to%20visit%20the%20state%20after%2015%20days%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20fulfil%20that%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20and%20central%20forces%20conducted%20a%20flag%20march%20in%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Kakching%2C%20Thoubal%2C%20and%20Imphal%20West%20District.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700498682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20221121%2FYA1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftwo-kuki-men-killed-in-fresh-violence-in-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20were%20reportedly%20village%20volunteers%20and%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftwo-kuki-men-killed-in-fresh-violence-in-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20tanks%20surround%20north%20Gaza's%20Indonesian%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700498626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci