the%20help%20of%20the%20Auger%20machine.%20We%20have%20reached%2022%20meters%20and%20we%20are%20going%20ahead%20rapidly.%20There%20is%20a%20lifeline%20pipe%20for%20sending%20food%20and%20other%20necessary%20items.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20have%20been%20given%20dry%20fruits%2C%20puffed%20rice%20and%20nuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98First%20breakthrough%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20evening%20that%20rescuers%20were%20able%20to%20push%20through%20a%20six-inch-wide%20pipeline%20through%20the%20rubble%20of%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%2C%20a%20breakthrough%20that%20will%20help%20them%20supply%20larger%20quantities%20of%20food%20and%20possibly%20allow%20live%20visuals%20of%20the%2041%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20for%20eight%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20achievement%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20told%20PTI%20after%20the%20installation%20of%20a%206-inch%20pipe%20in%20the%20tunnel%20on%20Monday%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%20have%20to%20accomplish%20the%20second%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20vital%20one.%20When%20they%20receive%20food%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20feel%20a%20bit%20better%20psychologically%2C%20and%20we%20will%20also%20try%20to%20establish%20communication%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20collapse%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20achievement.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20to%20accomplish%20the%20second%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20vital%20one.%20When%20they%20receive%20food%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20feel%20a%20bit%20better%20psychologically%2C%20and%20we%20will%20also%20try%20to%20establish%20communication%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20an%20official%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXM2buYaWsd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXM2buYaWsd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1726573419045519859%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL)%20director%20Anshu%20Manish%20Khalkho%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20breakthrough%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20site%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20sent%20the%20pipe%2053%20metres%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20rubble%20and%20the%20trapped%20workers%20can%20hear%20and%20experience%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3EPTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20send%20food%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20charger%20to%20the%20people%20who%20are%20trapped%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20We%20will%20also%20try%20to%20install%20a%20WiFi%20connection%20inside.%20DRDO%20robots%20are%20also%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20NHIDCL%20General%20Manager%20Colonel%20Deeapk%20Patil%2C%20who%20is%20heading%20the%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1726615871546892766%5C%22%3Etold%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20tunnelling%20expert%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20has%20been%20roped%20in%20for%20the%20rescue%20efforts%20by%20authorities%2C%20expressed%20satisfaction%20at%20the%20efforts%20so%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2F