(ONGC)%20to%20be%20transported%20to%20the%20top%2C%20per%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1978314%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20evening%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%2C%20the%20first%20machine%20of%20the%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20Limited%20(SJVNL%2C%20a%20Central%20Public%20Sector%20Enterprise%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Power)%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20vertical%20rescue%20tunnel%20has%20already%20reached%20the%20tunnel%20site%20and%20operations%20are%20being%20commenced%20post%20completion%20of%20access%20road%20by%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation.%20Movement%20of%20two%20other%20machines%20for%20the%20vertical%20tunnel%20construction%20have%20also%20started%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20Odisha%20by%20road%2C%20per%20the%20release.%20The%20machinery%20for%20vertical%20boring%20is%20being%20mobilised%20by%20the%20ONGC%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Ghaziabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20work%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20rescue%20tunnel%20of%20480%20metres%20from%20the%20Barkot%20end%20by%20THDC%20India%20Limited%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Power%20has%20also%20commenced%2C%20the%20release%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700497219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20180954%2FF_YKMLCaQAEAnv-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-new-rescue-plans-to-be-put-to-action-say-reports%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20parallel%20tunnels%20will%20now%20act%20as%20a%20route%20of%20escape%2C%20new%20reports%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-new-rescue-plans-to-be-put-to-action-say-reports%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUr