0a%20series%20of%20drones%20and%20missiles%20towards%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsraeli%20ships%20are%20legitimate%20targets%20for%20us%20anywhere...and%20we%20will%20not%20hesitate%20to%20take%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20General%20Ali%20Al-Moshki%2C%20a%20Huthi%20military%20official%2C%20told%20the%20group's%20Al-Massirah%20TV%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20also%20said%20Huthi%20threats%20to%20shipping%20around%20the%20Bab%20al-Mandab%20Strait%2C%20a%20choke-point%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20commercially%20vital%20Red%20Sea%2C%20were%20likely%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bahamas-flagged%2C%20British-owned%20Galaxy%20Leader%20is%20operated%20by%20a%20Japanese%20firm%20but%20has%20links%20to%20Israeli%20businessman%20Abraham%20%26quot%3BRami%26quot%3B%20Ungar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%C2%A0said%20the%20capture%20was%20in%20retaliation%20for%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20sparked%20by%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20militants%20who%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20and%20took%20about%20240%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2013%2C000%20people%20have%20since%20been%20killed%20in%20Israel's%20aerial%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20the%20territory's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunday's%20ship%20seizure%20%26quot%3Bis%20only%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20Huthi%20spokesman%20Mohammed%20Abdul-Salam%20said%20Sunday%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20pledging%20further%20maritime%20attacks%20until%20Israel%20halts%20its%20Gaza%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran-style%20boarding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaritime%20security%20company%20Ambrey%20said%20it%20had%20learned%20that%20the%20rebels%20boarded%20the%20ship%20by%20rappelling%20or%20sliding%20down%20a%20rope%20from%20a%20helicopter%20--%20the%20method%20used%20by%20Iran%20during%20previous%20vessel%20seizures%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%20headed%20from%20Turkey%20to%20India%20was%20re-routed%20to%20the%20Yemeni%20port%20of%20Salif%20port%20in%20Hodeida%20province%2C%20according%20to%20Ambrey%20and%20a%20Yemeni%20maritime%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbrey%20said%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Leader%2C%20which%20transports%20cars%20and%20other%20vehicles%2C%20is%20listed%20as%20Britain's%20Ray%20Car%20Carriers%20whose%20parent%20company%20belongs%20to%20Ungar%2C%20the%20Israeli%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20the%20seizure%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20grave%20incident%20of%20global%20consequence%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20a%20US%20military%20official%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20international%20law%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20were%20reportedly%20%26quot%3Bunder%20investigation%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Houthis%2C%20Ambrey%20said.%20They%20include%20Ukrainians%2C%20Bulgarians%2C%20Filipinos%2C%20Mexicans%20and%20a%20Romanian%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20and%20Romananian%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENippon%20Yusen%2C%20also%20known%20as%20NYK%20Line%20of%20Japan%2C%20said%20it%20had%20set%20up%20a%20task%20team%20to%20gather%20information%20and%20ensure%20the%20crew's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Yoko%20Kamikawa%20said%20Tokyo%20was%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20approaching%20the%20Houthis%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20communicating%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20urging%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Oman%2C%20Iran%20and%20other%20countries%20concerned%20to%20strongly%20urge%20the%C2%A0Houthis%20for%20the%20early%20release%20of%20the%20vessel%20and%20crew%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Threat%20likely%20to%20rise'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20of%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20characterised%20the%20capture%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BIranian%20attack%20against%20an%20international%20vessel%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20accusation%20dismissed%20by%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20repeatedly%20announced%20that%20the%20resistance%20groups%20in%20the%20region%20represent%20their%20countries%20and%20make%20decisions%20and%20act%20based%20on%20the%20interests%20of%20their%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Iran's%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesman%20Nasser%20Kanani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYemen's%20coastline%20overlooks%20the%20Bab%20al-Mandab%20Strait%20--%20a%20narrow%20pass%20between%20Yemen%20and%20Djibouti%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%20--%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20shipping%20lanes%2C%20and%20carries%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20global%20oil%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20of%20disruption%20to%20shipping%20in%20the%20wider%20region%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%2C%26quot%3B%20Torbjorn%20Soltvedt%20of%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20firm%20Verisk%20Maplecroft%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20security%20concerns%20compel%20shipping%20companies%20to%20avoid%20the%20Bab%20al-Mandab%20Strait%2C%20the%20result%20will%20be%20significantly%20higher%20costs%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20alternative%20routes.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20al-Basha%2C%20senior%20Middle%20East%20analyst%20for%20the%20US-based%20Navanti%20Group%20said%20the%20failure%20of%20Huthi%20missile%20and%20drone%20launches%20to%20hit%20targets%20inside%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bmight%20have%20influenced%20the%20decision%20to%20refocus%20on%20the%20Red%20Sea%20arena%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700492340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6gak0id8_