.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShanthi%20works%20with%20the%20Aravani%20Art%20Project%20which%20works%20with%20the%20transgender%20community%20to%20sensitise%20people%20through%20mural%20art.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanthi%20discovered%20her%20identity%20when%20she%20met%20a%20trans%20person.%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%20when%20I%20was%20weeping%20outside%20the%20shop%2C%20she%20came%20to%20me%20and%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%98Hey%20girl%2C%20how%20are%20you%3F%E2%80%99%20Her%20referring%20to%20me%20as%20a%20girl%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20felt%20somebody%20understood%20me%20for%20who%20I%20was%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20Shanthi%20came%20out%20to%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20could%20not%20believe%20it%2C%20she%20reasoned%20that%20she%20had%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20boy%2C%20how%20could%20this%20happen%20to%20me%20then%3F%20As%20per%20them%2C%20the%20last%20resort%20was%20to%20get%20me%20married.%20They%20did%20not%20understand%20me.%20I%20kept%20weeping%20but%20nobody%20cared.%20I%20even%20thought%20of%20taking%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2021%2C%20Shanthi%20joined%20the%20trans%20community%20and%20turned%20to%20sex%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20life%20took%20a%20U-turn%20when%20she%20was%20invited%20by%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20research%20institute%20to%20come%20out%20in%20public%20to%20share%20her%20story.%20Listening%20to%20it%2C%20Shanthi%20was%20offered%20a%20job%20as%20a%20radio%20jockey%20by%20a%20community%20radio%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20radio.%20Within%20a%20week%2C%20I%20learnt%20eve