.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20overflowing%20with%20a%20lakh%20of%20people%2C%20were%20speaking%20out%20loud%2C%20even%20if%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20had%20gone%20silent.%20The%20defeat%20had%20left%20them%20speechless%2C%20the%20Australian%20celebrations%20blind.%20In%20this%20collective%20expression%20of%20mourning%2C%20they%20had%20forgotten%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20superior%20skills%20and%20brilliant%20tactics%20of%20the%20rival%20team.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20not%20only%20had%20the%20invincibility%20of%20this%20Indian%20team%20been%20shattered%20but%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20their%20own%20identity%20had%20been%20ripped%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20362px)%2085vw%2C%20362px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22362%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%20976w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-244x300.jpg%20244w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-833x1024.jpg%20833w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22445%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%2C%20I%20was%20at%20a%20television%20news%20debate%20on%20whether%20this%20was%20the%20best%20white-ball%20team%20India%20has%20ever%20had.%20The%20consensus%20was%20yes%2C%20it%20is.%20I%20met%20a%20wealthy%20Indian%20cricket%20fan%2C%20there%20for%20one%20of%20the%20many%20debates%20the%20news%20channel%20had%20lined%20up%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%20final.%20I%20presume%20he%20was%20wealthy%20because%20he%20had%20bought%20the%20cricket%20bat%20with%20which%20Dhoni%20hit%20the%20six%20that%20won%20the%202011%20World%20Cup.%20He%20had%20spent%201%20lakh%20pounds%20(around%20Rs%201%20crore)%20to%20acquire%20that%20memorabilia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20been%20to%20most%20World%20Cup%20finals%20and%20was%20now%20making%20plans%20to%20go%20to%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20tickets%20were%20selling%20in%20black%20for%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20and%20hotels%20were%20beyond%20the%20common%20man%E2%80%99s%20reach.%20He%20was%20sure%20India%20had%20the%20best%20chance%20now%20to%20add%20to%20the%20two%20World%20Cups%20it%20has%20already%20won%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20because%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%20strong%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20inspirational%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20touching%20faith%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20infallibility%20and%20the%20Indian%20team%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20cricket%20fan%20I%20had%20met%20after%20India%20had%20decimated%20Afghanistan%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20was%20not%20worried%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20chances%20as%20he%20was%20sure%20India%20would%20be%20in%20the%20final%20at%20Ahmedabad%20and%20to%20defeat%20the%20team%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20was%20an%20impossibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20seen%20the%20steam%20billowing%20out%20of%20the%20collective%20energy%20of%20the%20thousands%20that%20day%20inside%20the%20Jaitley%20stadium%20and%20had%20wondered%20how%20they%20would%20react%20to%20an%20Indian%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20the%201996%20World%20Cup%20semifinals%20at%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20advertising%20blitz%20around%20the%20Indian%20campaign%20convinced%20people%20that%20the%20cup%20and%20India%20are%20made%20for%20each%20other.%20On%20that%20night%2C%20the%20Eden%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Paradise%20that%20the%20fans%20had%20envisaged%20%E2%80%93%20turned%20into%20an%20inferno%20as%20the%20Indian%20batting%20collapsed%20against%20the%20eventual%20winners%20Sri%20Lanka.%20The%20angry%20crowds%20went%20berserk%2C%20the%20sky%20lit%20up%20with%20fire%20as%20newspapers%20were%20lit%20and%20the%20ground%20was%20showered%20with%20litter.%20The%20match%20was%20abandoned%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20Indians%2C%20were%20declared%20the%20victors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20is%20no%201996.%20A%20cricket%20fan%20is%20now%20a%20greater%20political%20animal%20and%20his%20belief%20of%20invincibility%20stems%20from%20reasons%20beyond%20cricket.%20In%20this%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20even%20sports%20seem%20an%20extension%20of%20a%20narrative%20where%20the%20lines%20between%20self-belief%20and%20self-delusion%20have%20become%20blurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20thousands%20marched%20into%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2019%2C%20they%20were%20convinced%20that%20cricket%20and%20their%20political%20leadership%20had%20aligned%20the%20stars%20so%20perfectly%20that%20defeat%20was%20an%20unthinkable%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20had%20other%20ideas.%20They%20had%20studied%20and%20dissected%20the%20Indian%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20to%20perfection.%20They%20had%20even%20assessed%20the%20pitch%20conditions%20and%20the%20psychology%20of%20the%20highly%20partisan%20crowd%20well.%20What%20they%20unleashed%20on%20India%20was%20an%20exhibition%20of%20skills%2C%20planning%20and%20strategy%20that%20wore%20down%20a%20strong%20Indian%20team%20who%20despite%20their%20undeniable%20brilliance%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20really%20tested%20in%20their%20very%20vulnerable%20moments.%20To%20borrow%20from%20boxing%20terminology%2C%20Australia%20sparred%20first%20and%20once%20Indian%20defences%20were%20exposed%2C%20they%20unleashed%20a%20barrage%20of%20punches%20that%20left%20their%20opponents%20shell-shocked.%20Panic%20and%20pressure%2C%20something%20the%20Indians%20had%20appeared%20immune%20to%20so%20far%2C%20surfaced%20all%20of%20a%20sudden.%20A%20screaming%20sea%20of%20people%20were%20slowly%20losing%20their%20voice%20and%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20arrived%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20India%20had%20lost%20the%20plot.%20What%20was%20made%20for%20each%20other%20was%20now%20coming%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australians%20were%20stamping%20all%20over%20the%20Indians.%20The%20crowd%20was%20not%20there%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match.%20They%20were%20there%20to%20celebrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20win%2C%20not%20to%20applaud%20the%20wonderful%20cricket%20the%20Australians%20were%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20even%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presence%20could%20lift%20their%20spirits%20as%20all%20along%20they%20had%20believed%20he%20was%20the%20talisman%20that%20would%20ensure%20India%E2%80%99s%20win.%20Their%20world%20had%20collapsed%2C%20their%20dreams%20broken%20to%20shreds.%20They%20must%20have%20felt%20cheated%2C%20refusing%20to%20appreciate%20a%20four%20hit%2C%20a%20six%20struck%2C%20a%20century%20made%20and%20a%20victory%20achieved%20against%20all%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20captain%20had%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%20said%20that%20they%20would%20draw%20energy%20from%20silencing%20the%20crowd.%20The%20hush%20that%20descended%20on%20the%20stadium%20Sunday%20night%20even%20while%20Cummins%20lifted%20the%20trophy%20may%20have%20pleased%20the%20Australian%20captain%2C%20but%20it%20sure%20had%20diminished%20India%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700486980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crowd%20was%20not%20there%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match.%20They%20were%20there%20to%20celebrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20win%2C%20not%20to%20applaud%20the%20wonderful%20cricket%20the%20Australians%20were%20playing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A446%