%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESabu%20collects%20wild%20orchids%20that%20grow%20on%20tree%20trunks%2C%20rocks%2C%20and%20rock%20fissures.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20protecting%20these%20wild%20orchids%2C%20Sabu%20says%2C%20is%20an%20uphill%20task.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20collect%20and%20replant%20these%20orchids%20in%20forests%20as%20these%20need%20to%20be%20planted%20near%20streams%2C%20rocky%20areas%2C%20and%20tree%20trunks.%20I%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20tiny%20plants%20do%20not%20get%20washed%20away%20during%20disasters%20or%20heavy%20rain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20problem%2C%20Sabu%20plants%20these%20delicate%20blooms%20on%20the%20trunk%20of%20coffee%20plantations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grow%20orchids%20on%20coffee%20trunks%20as%20these%20plants%20do%20not%20grow%20on%20trees%20with%20thick%20foliage.%20It%20is%20easier%20to%20fix%20the%20plant%20roots%20of%20orchids%20on%20the%20soft%20trunk%20of%20coffee%20plants.%20Coffee%20plantations%20allow%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20diffused%20sunlight%20to%20stream%20in%20on%20them%20every%20day.%20Here%2C%20orchids%20are%20protected%20by%20direct%20harsh%20sunlight%20and%20heavy%20rain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20he%20has%20replanted%20around%20200%20saplings%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3