%20and%20botanists%20from%2020%20institutions%20who%20regularly%20visit%20his%20home%20to%20study%20wild%20orchids.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20these%20students%20find%20wild%20orchids%20in%20their%20textbooks.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20practically%20see%20these%20rare%20varieties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20work%2C%20Sabu%20was%20selected%20as%20the%20third-best%20farmer%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%20in%202021%20and%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Udhyana%20Shrestha%20Award%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20Agriculture%20Department%20in%202022.%20This%20year%2C%20he%20received%20the%20Best%20Farmer%20Award%20from%20the%20Horticulture%20Department%20of%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20have%20any%20selfish%20motive%20behind%20this%20initiative.%20Unlike%20others%2C%20I%20do%20not%20sell%20wild%20orchids%20to%20make%20money.%20I%20do%20it%20as%20part%20of%20conservation%20efforts.%20Conserving%20these%20wild%20orchids%20is%20paramount%20as%20future%20generations%20should%20also%20be%20able%20to%20cherish%20and%20enjoy%20the%20legacy%20in%20the%20same%20way%20I%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20V%20U%20Sabu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700227819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20time%20when%20India%20is%20losing%20its%20rare%20ornamental%20wild%20orchids%2C%20Kerala's%20V%20U%20Sabu%20has%20conserved%20120%20varieties%20of%20these%20exotic%20plants%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Wayanad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334357%2Fkerala-farmer-v-u-sabu-conserves-rare-wild-orchids-from-western-ghats-wayanad%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Bes