ia.com%2F297977%2Fex-banker-turns-barren-land-into-apple-orchard-in-himachal-kalasan-nursery-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different%20for%20the%20people%20that%20employ%20the%20people%20from%20my%20village.%20This%20is%20where%20Igloo%20Sethan%20Village%20was%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Igloo%20Man%20of%20Himachal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%2C%20much%20like%20us%2C%20harboured%20a%20fascination%20with%20Igloos%20and%20the%20way%20Eskimos%20lived%2C%20but%20the%20compelling%20need%20to%20generate%20an%20income%20in%20his%20village%20propelled%20him%20to%20embark%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20crafting%20these%20snow%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20location%20is%20just%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279810%2Fbest-budget-hostel-in-manali-offbeat-destination-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%20km%20from%20Manali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20Hampta%20Pass.%20Tourism%20was%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20livelihood%20in%20this%20area.%20While%20we%20had%20a%20summer%20home%20there%20for%20our%20family%20retreats%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20highways%20and%20overall%20development%20in%202005%20posed%20challenges%20for%20tourists%20to%20access%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCoSQy0hpCRJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCoSQy0hpCRJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22