%20conveys%20so%20many%20interesting%20things%20to%20me.%20It%20talks%20about%20coexistence%20very%20nicely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inclusion%20of%20a%20historic%20sculpture%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20adds%20a%20different%20dimension%20to%20the%20concept.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20here%20we%20are%2C%20seeing%20a%20spider%20%E2%80%94%20a%20smaller%20and%20less%20attended%20life%20form.%20So%2C%20for%20me%2C%20this%20one%20served%20the%20purpose%20of%20art%2C%20concept%2C%20conservation%20and%20science%20very%20nicely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFreezing%20moments%20in%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20of%202020%20was%20a%20life-changing%20one%20for%20Vihaan%2C%20who%20had%20just%20discovered%20the%20wonders%20of%20the%20camera.%20His%20father%E2%80%99s%20farm%20in%20Basavani%20village%2C%20which%20lay%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20was%20akin%20to%20a%20sanctuary%20for%20Vihaan.%20There%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296104%2Findia-first-selfie-by-maharaja-bir-chandra-of-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplenty%20to%20photograph%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhotographs%20meant%20I%20could%20watch%20the%20insects%20and%20animals%20even%20after%20I%20went%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vihaan%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ability%20to%20freeze%20moments%20in%20time%20and%20carry%20them%20with%20him%20through%20life%20compelled%20Vihaan%20to%20venture%20into%20photography.%20As%20his%20father%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20handed%20over%20my%20old%20DSLR%20camera%20to%20Vihaan%2C%20I%20was%20not%20expecting%20much%20from%20him.%20I%20intended%20to%20introduce%20him%20to%20nature%20so%20that%20he%20would%20start%20observing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20his%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%20Vihaan%20picked%20up%20photography%20very%20quickly.%20His%20images%20were%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%2